CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 20, 2014

[Cite as 05/20/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-2135.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2014-0049. State v. Hartman.

Medina App. No. 12CA0057-M, 2013-Ohio-4407. This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing of appellanVcross-appellee’s motion to strike notice of cross-appeal and memorandum in support of jurisdiction. It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied as moot.
